headline: Luvs Teams Up with Feeding America® to Support Families This Holiday Season
summary: CINCINNATI, November 13, 2024--Luvs, a trusted diaper brand under Procter & Gamble, is excited to announce its continued partnership with Feeding America®, the nation’s largest hunger-relief organization, to help families this holiday season. This year, Luvs will donate more than 225,000 Luvs Platinum Protection diapers to two U.S. cities in need, Cincinnati and Milwaukee, ensuring that more families have access to the essentials they need to thrive.
